high_descs: Turn right and left into the kitchen and go to the shelf.
Pick up the banana on the bookshelf.
Turn around and go to the fridge behind you.
Put the banana in the refrigerator and take the banana out.
Turn right and go to the diningtable and stand on the side with the bookshelf on your left while facing the diningtable.
Place the banana to the right of the knife on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled Banana on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, turn left and then proceed to turn left towards the shelf
